context: The patient was taken to the operating room and prepped and draped in the usual fashion after induction of general endotracheal anesthesia
The adenoid tissue was fulgurated with the suction Bovie set at 35
The anterior tonsillar pillars were infiltrated with 0.5% Marcaine and epinephrine.
Using the radiofrequency wand, the tonsils were ablated bilaterally
